headline.print_headline: Gasol, Randolph Lead Grizzlies Over Pelicans 93-81
headline.main: Gasol and Randolph Lead Grizzlies Past Pelicans

lead_paragraph: Marc Gasol scored 16 points, Zach Randolph had 15, and Memphis extended its winning streak at home to a franchise-record 16 straight.
